    {
      "text": "A 7-month-old infant with Tetralogy of Fallot is brought to the emergency department by her parents because of a 1-day history of fever, cough, and difficulty breathing. She was born at 29 weeks of gestation. Her routine immunizations are up-to-date. She is currently in the 4th percentile for length and 2nd percentile for weight. She appears ill. Her temperature is 39.1°C (102.3°F). Physical examination shows diffuse wheezing, subcostal retractions, and bluish discoloration of the fingertips. Administration of which of the following would most likely have prevented this patient's current condition?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Ribavirin"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Oseltamivir"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Ganciclovir"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Interferon-α"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Ceftriaxone"
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "text": "Nirsevimab"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 6,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-section-id=\"wBXh100\" data-sememe-id=\"FWYgML\">Ribavirin</a></span> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oo001S&anker=Zb0cfaa810fa91af5d3be01bf6564bee8\" data-learningcard-id=\"oo001S\" data-anker=\"Zb0cfaa810fa91af5d3be01bf6564bee8\" data-section-id=\"wLch-10\" data-sememe-id=\"0qbeCu\">guanosine</a> analog that is mainly used in combination therapy to treat <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lS0v-2&anker=Z5917fb5ac1ad1902eb48a7e3fc736c08\" data-learningcard-id=\"lS0v-2\" data-anker=\"Z5917fb5ac1ad1902eb48a7e3fc736c08\" data-sememe-id=\"C40qlT\">hepatitis C</a></span>. Although it may be indicated for the treatment of severe <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a></span> infection in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=x50Emg&anker=Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-anker=\"Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-section-id=\"h_XcL00\" data-sememe-id=\"P2YW3o\">immunocompromised</a> children, it has no role in the prophylaxis of such an infection.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z753d9f9846fe78f2b4651ac6605f7488\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z753d9f9846fe78f2b4651ac6605f7488\" data-section-id=\"9BXN100\" data-sememe-id=\"vWYAML\">Oseltamivir</a></span> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z89f9dee787a2ac2814ff9b5d782ba75d\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z89f9dee787a2ac2814ff9b5d782ba75d\" data-section-id=\"9BXN100\" data-sememe-id=\"DWY1nL\">neuraminidase inhibitor</a> used to treat and prevent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z9f0876a200701e5fdece2e58aa965574\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z9f0876a200701e5fdece2e58aa965574\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"SYcyoa0\">influenza A</a> and B <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Zcdc83877f75d9d9b9a07ece6544f646c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Zcdc83877f75d9d9b9a07ece6544f646c\" data-section-id=\"VacGja0\">virus</a> infection in children and adults. Although <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z963b513104666930093d4b4f3e4a5579\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z963b513104666930093d4b4f3e4a5579\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"XOY9I6\">influenza virus</a> may cause <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oL00Ag&anker=Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-learningcard-id=\"oL00Ag\" data-anker=\"Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-sememe-id=\"g90F5R\">bronchiolitis</a></span>, as seen in this <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=a40Q3T&anker=Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-learningcard-id=\"a40Q3T\" data-anker=\"Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-section-id=\"_8X56-\" data-sememe-id=\"4Qb3wt\">infant</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a> is a far more common causative agent. Moreover, as this <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=a40Q3T&anker=Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-learningcard-id=\"a40Q3T\" data-anker=\"Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-section-id=\"_8X56-\" data-sememe-id=\"4Qb3wt\">infant</a>'s immunizations are reported to be up to date, she must have been vaccinated against <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z963b513104666930093d4b4f3e4a5579\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z963b513104666930093d4b4f3e4a5579\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"XOY9I6\">influenza virus</a></span> at 6 months of age. Since <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a> lacks <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Bm0z3g&anker=Za56e82a5be27476816e0445bc25ef4c7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Bm0z3g\" data-anker=\"Za56e82a5be27476816e0445bc25ef4c7\" data-section-id=\"BDbzgD\" data-sememe-id=\"oOX0ty\">neuraminidase</a>, <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z753d9f9846fe78f2b4651ac6605f7488\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z753d9f9846fe78f2b4651ac6605f7488\" data-section-id=\"9BXN100\" data-sememe-id=\"vWYAML\">oseltamivir</a></span> is ineffective in the prevention or treatment of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oL00Ag&anker=Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-learningcard-id=\"oL00Ag\" data-anker=\"Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-sememe-id=\"g90F5R\">bronchiolitis</a>; in fact, it is thought to inhibit clearance of the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Zcdc83877f75d9d9b9a07ece6544f646c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Zcdc83877f75d9d9b9a07ece6544f646c\" data-section-id=\"VacGja0\">virus</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z760b55af39865361f98302102e25bdc4\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z760b55af39865361f98302102e25bdc4\" data-section-id=\"DBX1100\" data-sememe-id=\"JWYsmL\">Ganciclovir</a></span> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oo001S&anker=Zb0cfaa810fa91af5d3be01bf6564bee8\" data-learningcard-id=\"oo001S\" data-anker=\"Zb0cfaa810fa91af5d3be01bf6564bee8\" data-section-id=\"wLch-10\" data-sememe-id=\"0qbeCu\">guanosine</a> analog used in the treatment and prevention of infections with <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Mf0M52&anker=Zad44d620172736914bbe3c52435de665\" data-learningcard-id=\"Mf0M52\" data-anker=\"Zad44d620172736914bbe3c52435de665\" data-section-id=\"PpXWp_\" data-sememe-id=\"ynadDO\">cytomegalovirus</a></span>, particularly in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=x50Emg&anker=Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-anker=\"Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-section-id=\"h_XcL00\" data-sememe-id=\"P2YW3o\">immunocompromised</a> adults or transplant patients. It acts by inhibiting viral <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ko0U1S&anker=Zc702b4850395daf03ad0e79e5be4dbb0\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ko0U1S\" data-anker=\"Zc702b4850395daf03ad0e79e5be4dbb0\" data-section-id=\"_Lc5ZW0\" data-sememe-id=\"X2X9Tx\">DNA polymerase</a></span> after being activated by viral and cellular <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=n607lS&anker=Z5d1bc976d7a108b39404005e7da62e0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"n607lS\" data-anker=\"Z5d1bc976d7a108b39404005e7da62e0f\" data-section-id=\"hDccVe0\" data-sememe-id=\"eSXxAx\">kinases</a></span>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z760b55af39865361f98302102e25bdc4\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z760b55af39865361f98302102e25bdc4\" data-section-id=\"DBX1100\" data-sememe-id=\"JWYsmL\">Ganciclovir</a> is ineffective against <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Ze323fd45a9421157a7ba40795fda2d14\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Ze323fd45a9421157a7ba40795fda2d14\" data-section-id=\"Evc8be0\" data-sememe-id=\"OjcI0c0\">RNA viruses</a>, such as <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a></span>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4p03pS&anker=Z0e5f5a8300884d84de39914ba112e35e\" data-learningcard-id=\"4p03pS\" data-anker=\"Z0e5f5a8300884d84de39914ba112e35e\" data-section-id=\"D9c1pe0\" data-sememe-id=\"I2YYQo\">IFN-α</a></span> is an antiviral and immunomodulatory glycoprotein used to treat acute <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lS0v-2&anker=Z5917fb5ac1ad1902eb48a7e3fc736c08\" data-learningcard-id=\"lS0v-2\" data-anker=\"Z5917fb5ac1ad1902eb48a7e3fc736c08\" data-sememe-id=\"C40qlT\">hepatitis C</a> and chronic viral <span data-sememe-id=\"VpcGoW0\">hepatitis</span> (both <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z8045a0f1e7deea6f3ab44b70d77653d8\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z8045a0f1e7deea6f3ab44b70d77653d8\" data-section-id=\"gacFPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"TlY6w6\">HBV</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Zb66eecb323667f7d1b07e82259739553\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Zb66eecb323667f7d1b07e82259739553\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"9kYNJ6\">HCV</a>). It acts by inhibiting viral <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Jo0s1S&anker=Z4ad95da937229431881194f668aefdd2\" data-learningcard-id=\"Jo0s1S\" data-anker=\"Z4ad95da937229431881194f668aefdd2\" data-sememe-id=\"eJbxGu\">protein synthesis</a></span> and promoting the expression of <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=1K022S&anker=Zbbd425e91eaca4544cbd0132d6c872bd\" data-learningcard-id=\"1K022S\" data-anker=\"Zbbd425e91eaca4544cbd0132d6c872bd\" data-section-id=\"0qceCW0\" data-sememe-id=\"K2YUio\">MHC class I</a></span> molecules. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4p03pS&anker=Z0e5f5a8300884d84de39914ba112e35e\" data-learningcard-id=\"4p03pS\" data-anker=\"Z0e5f5a8300884d84de39914ba112e35e\" data-section-id=\"D9c1pe0\" data-sememe-id=\"I2YYQo\">IFN-α</a> has no role in the treatment or prevention of <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a></span> infection.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Zac33714c20522712f23f517fc3bbb806\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Zac33714c20522712f23f517fc3bbb806\" data-section-id=\"WjcPzX0\" data-sememe-id=\"Ulabwk\">Ceftriaxone</a></span> is used to treat gram-negative and gram-positive bacterial infections. This patient with unrepaired <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Oo0IXS&anker=Z829d94951879372f04d8e95e7b3c7058\" data-learningcard-id=\"Oo0IXS\" data-anker=\"Z829d94951879372f04d8e95e7b3c7058\" data-section-id=\"dMcon10\" data-sememe-id=\"0Caeq5\">Tetralogy of Fallot</a></span> is at high risk for bacterial <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mh0Vef&anker=Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-learningcard-id=\"mh0Vef\" data-anker=\"Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-sememe-id=\"rk0f6T\">pneumonia</a></span>. However, in the present infection, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Zac33714c20522712f23f517fc3bbb806\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Zac33714c20522712f23f517fc3bbb806\" data-section-id=\"WjcPzX0\" data-sememe-id=\"Ulabwk\">ceftriaxone</a> would not be used as prophylaxis but rather as empiric therapy. Although it can be difficult to distinguish bacterial <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mh0Vef&anker=Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-learningcard-id=\"mh0Vef\" data-anker=\"Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-sememe-id=\"rk0f6T\">pneumonia</a> from <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oL00Ag&anker=Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-learningcard-id=\"oL00Ag\" data-anker=\"Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-sememe-id=\"g90F5R\">bronchiolitis</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=a40Q3T&anker=Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-learningcard-id=\"a40Q3T\" data-anker=\"Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-section-id=\"_8X56-\" data-sememe-id=\"4Qb3wt\">infants</a>, the presence of diffuse <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Ze1c6d6b140663b2d56aebcff926e0252\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Ze1c6d6b140663b2d56aebcff926e0252\" data-section-id=\"8CXOFZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"DQb1yt\">wheezing</a> is more suggestive of <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oL00Ag&anker=Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-learningcard-id=\"oL00Ag\" data-anker=\"Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-sememe-id=\"g90F5R\">bronchiolitis</a></span>, which is typically caused by viral infections.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>F) CORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"wichtig\"><b><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Zf70f775456dbab554e5d7a3cb7965c7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Zf70f775456dbab554e5d7a3cb7965c7c\" data-section-id=\"3zWSsL0\" data-sememe-id=\"qsdCDr0\">Nirsevimab</a></b></span> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=gp0FKS&anker=Z86a7bedbcdf934db12cabdde22b280f6\" data-learningcard-id=\"gp0FKS\" data-anker=\"Z86a7bedbcdf934db12cabdde22b280f6\" data-section-id=\"u9cp6e0\" data-sememe-id=\"lBXva00\">monoclonal antibody</a> <span class=\"wichtig\"><b>against <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a> F protein</b></span>, used to prevent severe disease in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=a40Q3T&anker=Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-learningcard-id=\"a40Q3T\" data-anker=\"Z0fc257b9a869b8bf01b45c4fb73dbdc1\" data-section-id=\"_8X56-\" data-sememe-id=\"4Qb3wt\">infants</a> at high risk for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Z7dbad05f9d85b11c4ef01824174babcc\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Z7dbad05f9d85b11c4ef01824174babcc\" data-section-id=\"TzW6HL0\">severe RSV infection</a> (e.g., those with a history of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Fo0gdS&anker=Zce6ea5b5dc35124ab6b011ddf8481294\" data-learningcard-id=\"Fo0gdS\" data-anker=\"Zce6ea5b5dc35124ab6b011ddf8481294\" data-section-id=\"3KcSTW0\" data-sememe-id=\"qDaC25\">prematurity</a> and/or hemodynamically significant <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Up0bKS&anker=Z4e3e2c1885949b623580f92078d56c7d\" data-learningcard-id=\"Up0bKS\" data-anker=\"Z4e3e2c1885949b623580f92078d56c7d\">heart</a> disease). <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Z0a1076507e7ff84dea63cf64f2e92707\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Z0a1076507e7ff84dea63cf64f2e92707\" data-section-id=\"3zWSsL0\" data-sememe-id=\"BsdzCr0\">RSV prophylaxis</a> provides <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z074e24ca6749d89f915157e0041ec586\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z074e24ca6749d89f915157e0041ec586\" data-section-id=\"eyXxV00\" data-sememe-id=\"UdYb6L\">passive immunization</a> by neutralizing and inhibiting the fusion activity of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a>, which decreases viral replication. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Zf70f775456dbab554e5d7a3cb7965c7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Zf70f775456dbab554e5d7a3cb7965c7c\" data-section-id=\"3zWSsL0\" data-sememe-id=\"qsdCDr0\">Nirsevimab</a> is long acting, providing protection for 5 months, and is therefore typically administered during or just before <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Z4eaa489f5011e4c6f1dbe9d5ab6d9e2a\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Z4eaa489f5011e4c6f1dbe9d5ab6d9e2a\" data-section-id=\"gzWFHL0\" data-sememe-id=\"tsdX9r0\">RSV season</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Ze726974bb9fa328f0754a9bdfb0b694d\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Ze726974bb9fa328f0754a9bdfb0b694d\" data-section-id=\"3zWSsL0\" data-sememe-id=\"6yYjT7\">Palivizumab</a> can be used as an alternative, but because it is short acting, this drug must be administered monthly during <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=m80VM3&anker=Z4eaa489f5011e4c6f1dbe9d5ab6d9e2a\" data-learningcard-id=\"m80VM3\" data-anker=\"Z4eaa489f5011e4c6f1dbe9d5ab6d9e2a\" data-section-id=\"gzWFHL0\" data-sememe-id=\"tsdX9r0\">RSV season</a>.<br><br>Treatment of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Z30cf1c844b0e42bed39f00950cf3a137\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\" data-sememe-id=\"qkYCK6\">RSV</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oL00Ag&anker=Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-learningcard-id=\"oL00Ag\" data-anker=\"Z716391ad5739ddaaccad83a77d6e9f56\" data-sememe-id=\"g90F5R\">bronchiolitis</a> is primarily supportive, but <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-section-id=\"wBXh100\" data-sememe-id=\"FWYgML\">ribavirin</a> may be used in severely affected and/or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=x50Emg&anker=Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-anker=\"Z1af19ecc772907dd339670b5fb0e8b51\" data-section-id=\"h_XcL00\" data-sememe-id=\"P2YW3o\">immunosuppressed</a> children.</div>",
      "hint": "This infant presents with signs and symptoms suggestive of bronchiolitis (fever, cough, wheezing, subcostal retractions, acrocyanosis), which typically occurs in children less than 2 years old and is most commonly caused by respiratory syncytial virus (RSV) infection. Premature delivery and unrepaired congenital heart disease are risk factors for severe RSV infection.",
